{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1366055, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "理工科研究生用不上pad", "timestamp": 1617170200, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 好的，不买一票", "timestamp": 1617170240, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366069, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "单独的bilibili播放器不好吗\n\n其实iPad主要是用来代替笔记本做一些轻办公任务的，手写的话Apple Pencil现在独一档，除非上数位板之类的高级货，就算毕业之后用不到，拿来看剧也挺好的", "timestamp": 1617170251, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366082, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "手写什么场景需要呢？是不是刚需呢？", "timestamp": 1617170336, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366093, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 哈哈dz不怎么看B站", "timestamp": 1617170411, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 主要是想在ppt上做标注什么的\n之前觉得surface写字不行直接打字了，但是公式是个困难\n还有就是上课做题dz得抄题画图，看着有iPad的同学直接粘贴雨课堂的图记在iPad上觉得很香", "timestamp": 1617170629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366120, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就看手写了，如果手写是个刚需，值得买；不是的话就算了，Surface毕竟是Windows，做文档工作比iPad还是更方便", "timestamp": 1617170637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 买一票😂", "timestamp": 1617170667, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 嗯嗯买iPad我也不会不要surface的，我主力机啊😂", "timestamp": 1617170722, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366161, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哎其实我还有一个问题是我surface是不是使用不当，感觉挺多测评都觉得写的比较顺滑🤔dz的surface还是顶配。是不是因为装了Matlab这种就带不动手写这一块了", "timestamp": 1617170848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366170, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: LaTeX熟练的话可以直接打，我上课做笔记就是LaTeX，但确实怎么都赶不上手写快，这是真的，另外如果有其他的苹果设备，可以互相同步笔记，这也是优势吧，如果有条件买还是可以考虑下的，最低配的iPad+1代笔就足够了，续航肯定比Surface长", "timestamp": 1617170911, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "surface手写挺好呀 cz觉得ipad pro写字手感太硬", "timestamp": 1617171250, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366224, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我的配置：surface pro 5 + 手写笔 + 流畅的pdf编辑软件或onenote + snipaste软件(用于贴图)，特别香", "timestamp": 1617171372, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366234, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 谢谢bob！", "timestamp": 1617171450, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1366248, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: dz之前就用onenote来着，果然是我使用问题吗😭", "timestamp": 1617171538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1440202, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 268272, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换了一个笔尖，我的surface复活了！写字顺滑的不行，以前仿佛用的假笔（不过延迟还是有的但能接受", "timestamp": 1618226239, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 268272, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "有一个surface pro6觉得手写非常抖非常鸡肋想入iPad有必要吗\ndz大二，研究生是不是不怎么用iPad啊，会不会也就再用两年", "timestamp": 1617170099, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1618226238, "url": "", "vote": {}}}